snippet.title: YIIK: A Postmodern RPG (PS4, Vita, Wii U, PC) - PAX Prime Demo Gameplay
snippet.description:
We try out AckkStudios' upcoming RPG YIIK: A Postmodern RPG which feels like a modern Mother/Earthbound with a story that feels like its from the mind of David Lynch. Find out more on YIIK at http://www.yiikrpg.com

Check out AckkStudios on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfclSvnAiN5noff_kiwSVQg

http://excitehype.com
